{"type":"message","id":"34228259","parentId":"e929b9b6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:53:35.406Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_jFxKkssQkHcThgV9tHcwDbax","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\ndef load_config() -> Dict:\n    \"\"\"Load Tavily configuration from config file.\"\"\"\n    config_path = Path(__file__).parent.parent / \"config\" / \"tavily_config.json\"\n    \n    try:\n        with open(config_path) as f:\n            config = json.load(f)\n        return config\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[CONFIG] Error loading config: {e}\")\n        # Return default config\n        return {\n            \"api_key\": \"\",\n            \"defaults\": {\n                \"max_results\": 5,\n                \"search_depth\": \"basic\",\n                \"timeout\": 30,\n                \"cache_ttl_minutes\": 15\n            }\n        }\n\n\ndef register_with_watchdog(session_id: str, run_id: str, task_desc: str, \n                          expected_time: int, model: str = \"tavily-search\",\n                          runtime_type: str = \"search\") -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    Register a search operation with the agent watchdog.\n    \n    Args:\n        session_id: Unique session identifier\n        run_id: Unique run identifier\n        task_desc: Description of the task\n        expected_time: Expected runtime in seconds\n        model: Model name (default: \"tavily-search\")\n        runtime_type: Type of runtime (default: \"search\")\n    \n    Returns:\n        True if registration successful, False otherwise\n\n[371 more lines in file. Use offset=55 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773071615402}}
{"type":"message","id":"9cfd16df","parentId":"34228259","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:53:45.768Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ahora voy a modificar la función para expandir variables de entorno. Primero, voy a crear una función auxiliar para expandir variables:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_XybpvNzRaSKlDWdCvHy3Og3Y","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tavily-web-search/scripts/tavily_integrations.py","oldText":"def load_config() -> Dict:\n    \"\"\"Load Tavily configuration from config file.\"\"\"\n    config_path = Path(__file__).parent.parent / \"config\" / \"tavily_config.json\"\n    \n    try:\n        with open(config_path) as f:\n            config = json.load(f"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tavily-web-search/scripts/tavily_integrations.py\", \"oldText\": \"def load_config() -> Dict:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Load Tavily configuration from config file.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    config_path = Path(__file__).parent.parent / \\\"config\\\" / \\\"tavily_config.json\\\"\\n    \\n    try:\\n        with open(config_path) as f:\\n            config = json.load(f"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1773071615405,"errorMessage":"terminated"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b4c1cbd","parentId":"9cfd16df","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:54:21.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ahora voy a modificar la función `load_config` para expandir variables de entorno. Primero, voy a crear una función auxiliar para expandir variables:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2KZldeWEQ7v46hl4Quugaqg7","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tavily-web-search/scripts/tavily_integrations.py","oldText":"def load_config() -> Dict:\n    \"\"\"Load Tavily configuration from config file.\"\"\"\n    config_path = Path(__file__).parent.parent / \"config\" / \"tavily_config.json\"\n    \n    try:\n        with open(config_path) as f:\n            config = json.load(f)\n        return config\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[CONFIG] Error loading config: {e}\")\n        # Return default config\n        return {\n            \"api_key\": \"\",\n            \"defaults\": {\n                \"max_results\": 5,\n                \"search_depth\": \"basic\",\n                \"timeout\": 30,\n                \"cache_ttl_minutes\": 15\n            }\n        }","newText":"def expand_env_vars(value):\n    \"\"\"Expand environment variables in a string.\"\"\"\n    if isinstance(value, str) and value.startswith(\"${\") and value.endswith(\"}\"):\n        env_var = value[2:-1]\n        return os.environ.get(env_var, value)\n    return value\n\ndef deep_expand_env_vars(obj):\n    \"\"\"Recursively expand environment variables in a nested structure.\"\"\"\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        return {k: deep_expand_env_vars(v) for k, v in obj.items()}\n    elif isinstance(obj, list):\n        return [deep_expand_env_vars(item) for item in obj]\n    elif isinstance(obj, str):\n        return expand_env_vars(obj)\n    else:\n        return obj\n\ndef load_config() -> Dict:\n    \"\"\"Load Tavily configuration from config file and expand environment variables.\"\"\"\n    config_path = Path(__file__).parent.parent / \"config\" / \"tavily_config.json\"\n    \n    try:\n        with open(config_path) as f:\n            config = json.load(f)\n        \n        # Expand environment variables in the entire config\n        config = deep_expand_env_vars(config)\n        \n        # Special handling for API keys - check if they're still placeholders\n        if config.get(\"api_key\", \"\").startswith(\"${\"):\n            print(f\"[CONFIG] WARNING: API key not expanded: {config['api_key']}\")\n            print(f\"[CONFIG] Available env vars: TAVILY_API_KEY={os.environ.get('TAVILY_API_KEY', 'NOT SET')[:10]}...\")\n        \n        return config\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[CONFIG] Error loading config: {e}\")\n        # Return default config\n        return {\n            \"api_key\": os.environ.get(\"TAVILY_API_KEY\", \"\"),\n            \"defaults\": {\n                \"max_results\": 5,\n                \"search_depth\": \"basic\",\n                \"timeout\": 30,\n                \"cache_ttl_minutes\": 15\n            }\n        }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":42,"output":714,"cacheRead":45376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46132,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773071627840}}
