{"type":"message","id":"86885c71","parentId":"6ece87ba","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:01:10.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"¡Perdón! Me quedé esperando el resultado del comando. Voy a continuar con las correcciones restantes:\n\n## 2. **Workspace Janitor - Mejor práctica recomendada**\n\nLa mejor práctica sería crear un wrapper script en el workspace raíz que sirva como punto de entrada único. Esto es más óptimo porque:\n\n1. **Centraliza la invocación** en un solo lugar\n2. **Mantiene la compatibilidad** con `command-dispatch: workspace-janitor`\n3. **Facilita el mantenimiento** al tener un script principal claro\n4. **Permite validaciones** previas a la ejecución\n\nVoy a crear el wrapper script:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Z1WEkPGlpa3PBQu4KYJrDEmE","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-janitor","content":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\n#\n# Workspace Janitor Wrapper Script\n# Central entry point for workspace janitor functionality\n#\n\nset -e\n\nSCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"${BASH_SOURCE[0]}\")\" && pwd)\"\nJANITOR_DIR=\"$SCRIPT_DIR/skills/workspace-janitor\"\nSCRIPTS_DIR=\"$JANITOR_DIR/scripts\"\n\n# Colors for output\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nNC='\\033[0m' # No Color\n\nprint_info() {\n    echo -e \"${BLUE}[INFO]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\nprint_success() {\n    echo -e \"${GREEN}[SUCCESS]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\nprint_warning() {\n    echo -e \"${YELLOW}[WARNING]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\nprint_error() {\n    echo -e \"${RED}[ERROR]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\n# Check if janitor directory exists\nif [ ! -d \"$JANITOR_DIR\" ]; then\n    print_error \"Janitor skill directory not found: $JANITOR_DIR\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Check if scripts directory exists\nif [ ! -d \"$SCRIPTS_DIR\" ]; then\n    print_error \"Janitor scripts directory not found: $SCRIPTS_DIR\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Parse command line arguments\nACTION=\"${1:-scan}\"\nshift\n\ncase \"$ACTION\" in\n    scan|--scan|-s)\n        print_info \"Running workspace scan only (no deletion)\"\n        cd \"$SCRIPTS_DIR\"\n        python3 scan_workspace.py \"$@\"\n        ;;\n    \n    classify|--classify|-c)\n        print_info \"Running file classification\"\n        cd \"$SCRIPTS_DIR\"\n        python3 classify_files.py \"$@\"\n        ;;\n    \n    report|--report|-r)\n        print_info \"Generating cleanup report\"\n        cd \"$SCRIPTS_DIR\"\n        python3 generate_cleanup_report.py \"$@\"\n        ;;\n    \n    full|--full|-f)\n        print_info \"Running full janitor workflow (scan, classify, report)\"\n        cd \"$SCRIPTS_DIR\"\n        python3 scan_workspace.py\n        python3 classify_files.py\n        python3 generate_cleanup_report.py\n        ;;\n    \n    help|--help|-h)\n        echo \"Workspace Janitor - Safe workspace maintenance\"\n        echo \"\"\n        echo \"Usage: workspace-janitor [COMMAND] [OPTIONS]\"\n        echo \"\"\n        echo \"Commands:\"\n        echo \"  scan, -s      Scan workspace only (no deletion)\"\n        echo \"  classify, -c  Classify files\"\n        echo \"  report, -r    Generate cleanup report\"\n        echo \"  full, -f      Run full workflow (scan, classify, report)\"\n        echo \"  help, -h      Show this help message\"\n        echo \"\"\n        echo \"Examples:\"\n        echo \"  workspace-janitor scan\"\n        echo \"  workspace-janitor full\"\n        echo \"  workspace-janitor --help\"\n        ;;\n    \n    *)\n        print_warning \"Unknown action: $ACTION\"\n        print_info \"Running default scan action\"\n        cd \"$SCRIPTS_DIR\"\n        python3 scan_workspace.py \"$ACTION\" \"$@\"\n        ;;\nesac\n\nexit 0"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1738,"output":964,"cacheRead":45440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48142,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1