{"type":"message","id":"2b7d583f","parentId":"320619fd","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:13:02.609Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_1QuFSNdLHeTnpBCEAPZxOBju","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Active Projects Registry\n\n## OpenClaw Memory System\n- **Status**: In progress\n- **Tech Stack**: PostgreSQL, pgvector, Python, Gemini API\n- **Description**: Full memory stack upgrade with vector database, smart loading, and auto-curation\n- **Location**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/`\n- **URL**: N/A (local system)\n\n## Error Learning Loop\n- **Status**: Live\n- **Tech Stack**: Python, cron, semantic deduplication\n- **Description**: Autonomous incident capture, deduplication, and guardrail promotion system\n- **Location**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/error-learning-loop/`\n- **URL**: N/A (internal tool)\n\n## Workspace Janitor\n- **Status**: Live\n- **Tech Stack**: Python, file classification, cleanup automation\n- **Description**: Safe workspace maintenance with user-authorized cleanup\n- **Location**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/workspace-janitor/`\n- **URL**: N/A (internal tool)\n\n## Agent Watchdog\n- **Status**: Live\n- **Tech Stack**: Python, session monitoring, stall detection\n- **Description**: Monitors running agents and detects stalls for automatic recovery\n- **Location**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/`\n- **URL**: N/A (internal tool)\n\n## Salesforce Development Skills\n- **Status**: In progress\n- **Tech Stack**: Salesforce, Apex, LWC, Python analysis\n- **Description**: Production-ready skills for Salesforce architecture and code auditing\n- **Location**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-architect/`, `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-code-auditor/`\n- **URL**: N/A (skills development)\n\n---\n\n## Update Policy (Hardening CHANGE 8)\n**Conservative updates only:**\n- ✅ **Sufficient context exists** → Update normally\n- ⚠️ **Partial/uncertain context** → Preserve existing entries, mark uncertain rows with `[?]`\n- ❌ **Information too weak** → Ask user instead of overwriting\n\n**Before any overwrite:**\n1. Create backup in `memory/backups/`\n2. Log update in `memory_curation_log.md`\n\n**If projects.md becomes too large/noisy:**\n- Emit incident: `memory|QUALITY|projects_registry|too_large|needs_pruning`\n\n*Note: Please provide details about your active external projects for a more complete registry.*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773076382591}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7341124","parentId":"2b7d583f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:13:09.051Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_oLeYcoewMUhszUnjU7rR2Fbl","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":587,"output":73,"cacheRead":80192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80852,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773076382606}}
{"type":"message","id":"a9f15f12","parentId":"d7341124","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:13:09.099Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_oLeYcoewMUhszUnjU7rR2Fbl","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - Curated Long-Term Memory\n\n**Last updated: 2026-03-06**\n\n## Current Active Projects\n1. **OpenClaw Memory System** - ✅ 100% installed + ✅ 100% hardened\n2. **Error Learning Loop** - Autonomous incident capture and guardrail promotion (live)\n3. **Workspace Janitor** - Safe workspace cleanup automation (live + memory integration)\n4. **Agent Watchdog** - Agent stall detection and recovery (live + memory integration)\n5. **Salesforce Development Skills** - Architecture and code auditing tools (in progress)\n\n## System Configuration\n- **Primary Model**: deepseek-chat\n- **Reasoning Model**: deepseek-reasoner (fallback for complex tasks)\n- **Embeddings**: gemini/embedding-001 for semantic search\n- **Gateway**: Running with OpenClaw control UI\n\n## Recent Milestones\n- 2026-03-06: Full memory system upgrade completed (6 layers)\n- 2026-03-06: Hardening update applied (9 improvements)\n- 2026-03-06: Cron job updated to use hardened wrapper\n- 2026-03-06: Janitor configured for memory backup management\n- 2026-03-06: Error learning loop improvements completed\n- 2026-03-06: 1. agent-watchdog (completed) – integration successful, watchdog_orchestrator.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: 2. salesforce-architect (completed) – integration successful, utils_io.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: 3. salesforce-code-auditor (completed) – integration successful, generate_reports.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: 4. long-prompt-orchestrator (completed) – integration successful, learning_emit.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: Improvements sub-agent launched (613cc35a-a953-4491-8931-bc75e625a2a7) to implement:\n- 2026-03-06: ## Full Memory System Upgrade - COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY\n- 2026-03-06: 1. **Vector flush removed from heartbeat** - Heartbeat now local, fast, resilient\n- 2026-03-06: 2. ✅ **Tavily configured** - Added web search configuration to `openclaw.json`\n- unknown: ### 1. Removed Vector Flush from Heartbeat\n- unknown: - **After**: Vector flush removed from HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## Skills Inventory\n- error-learning-loop (production + memory incident integration)\n- workspace-janitor (production + memory backup management)\n- agent-watchdog (production + long memory task monitoring)\n- salesforce-architect (development)\n- salesforce-code-auditor (development)\n- long-prompt-orchestrator (development)\n\n## Guardrails & Learnings\n- Validator batch size limit: ≤5 items per validator\n- Handoff report enforcement: mandatory for all sub-agents\n- Deadlock detection: dependency cycle checking\n- Model stall prevention: watchdog registration for long-running tasks\n- Memory system: graceful degradation, safe backups, conservative updates"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773076389073}}
{"type":"message","id":"d371ea41","parentId":"a9f15f12","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:13:19.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"He cargado el contexto de memoria de manera eficiente según las instrucciones de HEARTBEAT.md. Revisando el estado actual:\n\n1. **Proyectos activos**: Estoy en medio del endurecimiento incremental de los skills de Salesforce\n2. **Estado del sistema**: Estable, trabajando en la Parte 5 del endurecimiento\n3. **Progreso actual**: He completado 4 de las 5 partes del trabajo de fundación (Clase A)\n4. **Próximos pasos**: Necesito completar la Parte 5 y luego proceder con las mejoras de comportamiento en tiempo de ejecución (Clase B)\n\nNo hay tareas pendientes en HEARTBEAT.md, no hay alertas urgentes. Estoy enfocado en completar el endurecimiento incremental de Salesforce según las instrucciones recibidas.\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":726,"output":185,"cacheRead":80832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81743,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773076389091}}
