{"type":"message","id":"e14800a9","parentId":"cebbbdc1","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:26:23.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ahora voy a agregar una sección sobre el comportamiento de enrutamiento de proyectos:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_I6GBrbBsypnbZuR9RX4MzbtX","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-architect/SKILL.md","offset":100,"limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":101,"output":116,"cacheRead":84288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84505,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773077174616}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef9c980f","parentId":"e14800a9","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:26:23.045Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_I6GBrbBsypnbZuR9RX4MzbtX","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Runtime Project Structure\nWhen executing the skill, a new project folder is created under `workspace/projects/<project_key>/` with the following layout:\n\n```\nworkspace/projects/<project_key>/\n├── discovery/\n│   ├── Discovery_Report.md\n│   ├── Discovery_Process_Analysis.md\n│   └── Discovery_QA.xlsx\n├── fit_gap/\n│   └── Fit_Gap_Matrix.xlsx\n├── design/\n│   └── Functional_Design.docx\n├── data_model/\n│   └── Data_Model.xlsx\n├── architecture/\n│   ├── Architecture_Overview.md\n│   └── Evidence_Log.md\n├── evidence/\n│   └── Evidence_Log.md (symlink or copy)\n└── README.md\n```\n\n## Pipeline Stages\n\n### Stage 0 – Intake Gate\n**Mandatory inputs** (block pipeline if missing):\n- Project name\n- Industry\n- Country\n- Salesforce clouds licensed\n- User count\n- Process description\n- Implementation scope\n\nIf any mandatory input is missing, generate discovery questions and stop.\n\n### Stage 1 – Discovery (EC0249)\nExtract actors, processes, events, systems, unknowns from transcripts/notes/SOW.\n**Outputs:**\n- `Discovery_Report.md`\n- `Discovery_Process_Analysis.md`\n- `Discovery_QA.xlsx`\n\n### Stage 2 – Requirements Consolidation\nTransform discovery into structured requirements with:\n- ID\n- Process\n- Actor\n- Description\n\n[124 more lines in file. Use offset=150 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773077183028}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e7b5407","parentId":"ef9c980f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:26:53.883Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Voy a agregar una sección sobre el comportamiento de enrutamiento endurecido después de la estructura del proyecto:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zxUuLH6NLft9K2QtOrpdY2xF","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-architect/SKILL.md","oldText":"└── README.md","newText":"└── README.md\n\n## HARDENED PROJECT ROUTING BEHAVIOR (RUNTIME ENFORCEMENT)\n\n### Project Owner Discipline\nThe architect acts as the **single governing skill** for all Salesforce work. Every execution must:\n\n1. **Identify project_key**: Extract or generate from request context\n2. **Check project existence**: Look for existing `workspace/projects/<project_key>/`\n3. **Create if missing**: Initialize with standard structure\n4. **Route all artifacts**: No Salesforce artifacts outside project folder\n5. **Classify request type**:\n   - New work (new project or phase)\n   - Artifact update (revision of existing)\n   - Review (architect validation)\n   - Correction (address issues)\n   - Code audit (technical validation)\n   - Remediation (fix audit findings)\n\n### Project README Governance\nThe architect must maintain and update `workspace/projects/<project_key>/README.md` with:\n\n```\n# Project: <project_key>\n\n## Current State: <state from state machine>\n- Entered: <timestamp>\n- Validated: <timestamp>\n\n## State History\n- DISCOVERY: <start> - <end>\n- REQUIREMENTS: <start> - <end>\n- FIT_GAP: <start> - <end>\n- DESIGN: <start> - <end>\n- DATA_MODEL: <start> - <end>\n- ARCH_REVIEW: <start> - <end>\n- CODE_AUDIT: <start> - <end>\n- REMEDIATION: <start> - <end>\n- FINALIZED: <start> - <end>\n\n## Artifact Versions\n- Discovery: v<version>\n- Requirements: v<version>\n- Fit/Gap: v<version>\n- Design: v<version>\n- Data Model: v<version>\n- Architecture Review: v<version>\n- Code Audit: v<version> (if exists)\n- Remediation: v<version> (if exists)\n\n## Code Audits\n- Case ID: <case_id>\n- Mode: <A/B/C>\n- Date: <timestamp>\n- Findings: <summary>\n- Status: <open/in remediation/closed>\n\n## Next Actions\n- [ ] Action 1\n- [ ] Action 2\n```\n\n### Artifact Containment Rule\n**NO Salesforce artifact may be created outside:**\n`<workspace>/projects/<project_key>/...`\n\n**Exceptions**: Only global references in `<workspace>/references/`\n\n**Violation response**: Emit incident `salesforce|PROJECT_ROUTING|artifact_outside_project|blocked`"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":384,"output":678,"cacheRead":84480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85542,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773077183043}}
