{"type":"message","id":"23338cf6","parentId":"db50b2cb","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:29:07.143Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_aDFFva0Ma9orBWBTOaUnlZHV","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`<workspace>/projects/<project_key>/code_audit/<case_id>/inputs/`\n\nSupported formats:\n- Apex `.cls`\n- Apex Triggers `.trigger`\n- LWC `.js`, `.html`, `.xml`\n- Visualforce `.page`\n- Metadata `.xml`\n- Flow metadata\n- DTO / integration classes\n\nThe skill **indexes files first instead of reading them immediately**.\n\n## Required Runtime Structure\n```\n<workspace>/projects/<project_key>/code_audit/<case_id>/\n  CASE.md\n  inputs/\n  work/\n  snippets/\n  temp_analysis/\n  outputs/\n  INDEX.md\n  MANIFEST.json\n  DEPENDENCY_GRAPH.json\n  ENTRYPOINTS.json\n  EXECUTION_TRACE.md\n  FINDINGS.md\n  TEST_MATRIX.md\n  AUDIT_REPORT.md\n```\n\n## Skill Directory Structure\n```\nskills/salesforce-code-auditor/\n  SKILL.md (this file)\n  scripts/\n    init_case.py\n    index_inputs.py\n    detect_entrypoints.py\n    build_dependency_graph.py\n    extract_snippets.py\n    generate_reports.py\n    utils_fs.py\n  references/\n    FILE_TYPES.md\n    REVIEW_CHECKLISTS.md\n    TOKEN_STRATEGY.md\n    REPORT_TEMPLATE.md\n  examples/\n\n[148 more lines in file. Use offset=150 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773080947122}}
{"type":"message","id":"abce549e","parentId":"23338cf6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:29:42.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Voy a agregar una sección sobre la integración con la máquina de estados:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0MqrN6aCiIU5EHm847m86fbl","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-code-auditor/SKILL.md","oldText":"## Skill Directory Structure\n```\nskills/salesforce-code-auditor/\n  SKILL.md (this file)\n  scripts/\n    init_case.py\n    index_inputs.py\n    detect_entrypoints.py\n    build_dependency_graph.py\n    extract_snippets.py\n    generate_reports.py\n    utils_fs.py\n  references/\n    FILE_TYPES.md\n    REVIEW_CHECKLISTS.md\n    TOKEN_STRATEGY.md\n    REPORT_TEMPLATE.md\n  examples/\n    example_intake.md\n    example_manifest.md\n    example_audit_report.md\n```","newText":"## Skill Directory Structure\n```\nskills/salesforce-code-auditor/\n  SKILL.md (this file)\n  scripts/\n    init_case.py\n    index_inputs.py\n    detect_entrypoints.py\n    build_dependency_graph.py\n    extract_snippets.py\n    generate_reports.py\n    utils_fs.py\n  references/\n    FILE_TYPES.md\n    REVIEW_CHECKLISTS.md\n    TOKEN_STRATEGY.md\n    REPORT_TEMPLATE.md\n  examples/\n    example_intake.md\n    example_manifest.md\n    example_audit_report.md\n```\n\n## PROJECT STATE MACHINE INTEGRATION\n\n### Audit Timing in Project Lifecycle\nAudits must align with project state from `SALESFORCE_PROJECT_STATE_MACHINE.md`:\n\n1. **DISCOVERY phase**: Mode A audits to understand current codebase\n2. **DESIGN phase**: Mode C audits to validate design feasibility\n3. **ARCH_REVIEW phase**: Mode B audits for architectural validation\n4. **CODE_AUDIT phase**: Formal audit as part of state progression\n5. **REMEDIATION phase**: Follow‑up audits to validate fixes\n\n### State Transition Impact\n- **CODE_AUDIT → ARCH_REVIEW**: Findings may require architectural changes\n- **ARCH_REVIEW → REMEDIATION**: Critical findings require remediation\n- **REMEDIATION → FINALIZED**: All blocking findings must be resolved\n- **Any state → CODE_AUDIT**: Can trigger audit at any phase if needed\n\n### Project README Integration\nThe auditor must update project README with audit information:\n\n```\n## Code Audits\n- Case ID: <case_id>\n- Mode: <A/B/C>\n- Date: <timestamp>\n- Findings: <summary>\n- Status: <open / in remediation / closed>\n\n## Audit History\n- <case_id_1>: <date> - <mode> - <status>\n- <case_id_2>: <date> - <mode> - <status>\n```"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":52282,"output":667,"cacheRead":35712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773080947132}}
