{"type":"message","id":"e0701404","parentId":"f329506d","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:51:22.595Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_oJCJFuFLkj28i3GZOnfAg5OT","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - Curated Long-Term Memory\n\n**Last updated: 2026-03-06**\n\n## Current Active Projects\n1. **OpenClaw Memory System** - ✅ 100% installed + ✅ 100% hardened\n2. **Error Learning Loop** - Autonomous incident capture and guardrail promotion (live)\n3. **Workspace Janitor** - Safe workspace cleanup automation (live + memory integration)\n4. **Agent Watchdog** - Agent stall detection and recovery (live + memory integration)\n5. **Salesforce Development Skills** - Architecture and code auditing tools (in progress)\n\n## System Configuration\n- **Primary Model**: deepseek-chat\n- **Reasoning Model**: deepseek-reasoner (fallback for complex tasks)\n- **Embeddings**: gemini/embedding-001 for semantic search\n- **Gateway**: Running with OpenClaw control UI\n\n## Recent Milestones\n- 2026-03-06: Full memory system upgrade completed (6 layers)\n- 2026-03-06: Hardening update applied (9 improvements)\n- 2026-03-06: Cron job updated to use hardened wrapper\n- 2026-03-06: Janitor configured for memory backup management\n- 2026-03-06: Error learning loop improvements completed\n- 2026-03-06: 1. agent-watchdog (completed) – integration successful, watchdog_orchestrator.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: 2. salesforce-architect (completed) – integration successful, utils_io.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: 3. salesforce-code-auditor (completed) – integration successful, generate_reports.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: 4. long-prompt-orchestrator (completed) – integration successful, learning_emit.py updated\n- 2026-03-06: Improvements sub-agent launched (613cc35a-a953-4491-8931-bc75e625a2a7) to implement:\n- 2026-03-06: ## Full Memory System Upgrade - COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY\n- 2026-03-06: 1. **Vector flush removed from heartbeat** - Heartbeat now local, fast, resilient\n- 2026-03-06: 2. ✅ **Tavily configured** - Added web search configuration to `openclaw.json`\n- unknown: ### 1. Removed Vector Flush from Heartbeat\n- unknown: - **After**: Vector flush removed from HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## Skills Inventory\n- error-learning-loop (production + memory incident integration)\n- workspace-janitor (production + memory backup management)\n- agent-watchdog (production + long memory task monitoring)\n- salesforce-architect (development)\n- salesforce-code-auditor (development)\n- long-prompt-orchestrator (development)\n\n## Guardrails & Learnings\n- Validator batch size limit: ≤5 items per validator\n- Handoff report enforcement: mandatory for all sub-agents\n- Deadlock detection: dependency cycle checking\n- Model stall prevention: watchdog registration for long-running tasks\n- Memory system: graceful degradation, safe backups, conservative updates"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773082282584}}
{"type":"message","id":"013981c9","parentId":"e0701404","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:51:39.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"He cargado el contexto de memoria de manera eficiente según las instrucciones de HEARTBEAT.md. Revisando el estado actual:\n\n1. **Proyectos activos**: Estoy en medio del endurecimiento incremental de Salesforce\n2. **Estado del sistema**: Estable, acabo de implementar mejoras basadas en tus instrucciones:\n   - ✅ **Parser estructurado**: Convertí referencias a YAML (`role_model.yaml`, `state_machine.yaml`)\n   - ✅ **Motor real de state machine**: Creé `state_machine_engine.py` con validación robusta\n   - ✅ **Validación determinística de DoD**: Creé `dod_validator.py` con reglas determinísticas\n   - 📝 **README/project control file**: Pendiente de implementar robusto\n\n3. **Progreso actual**: He implementado 3 de las 4 mejoras prioritarias que mencionaste\n4. **Próximo paso**: Implementar README/project control file robusto\n\nNo hay tareas pendientes en HEARTBEAT.md, no hay alertas urgentes. Estoy listo para implementar el sistema robusto de README/project control file.\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":28647,"output":260,"cacheRead":70528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99435,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773082282592}}
