pecialistas**: Documentar expectativas de DoD por rol\n4. **Monitoreo continuo**: Usar métricas para mejora iterativa\n\n### **Valor Entregado:**\n- **Gobierno robusto**: Sistema completo para control de proyectos Salesforce\n- **Calidad consistente**: Validación determinística de entregables\n- **Visibilidad total**: Estado del proyecto siempre actualizado y accesible\n- **Base para escala**: Arquitectura preparada para crecimiento\n\n---\n\n### Handoff Report Final\n- **Outcome**: success\n- **Incidents**: none\n- **Files touched**: 18 files (15 created, 3 updated)\n- **Next action**: Integrate hardened system with existing architect pipeline\n- **Watchdog fields**:\n  - session_id: main_hardening_upgrade_complete\n  - run_id: salesforce_hardening_final_2026_03_09\n  - last_activity_at: 2026-03-09T14:00:00\n  - progress_marker: all_priority_improvements_implemented\n\n**🎉 ENDURECIMIENTO INCREMENTAL DE SALESFORCE COMPLETADO EXITOSAMENTE**"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":60,"output":2951,"cacheRead":111360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773082787898}}
