{"type":"message","id":"ab52b04d","parentId":"45cd0932","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:57:35.661Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-09 16:54:05 EST] [Post-compaction context refresh]\nSystem: \nSystem: Session was just compacted. The conversation summary above is a hint, NOT a substitute for your startup sequence. Execute your Session Startup sequence now — read the required files before responding to the user.\nSystem: \nSystem: Critical rules from AGENTS.md:\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Every Session\nSystem: \nSystem: Before doing anything else:\nSystem: \nSystem: 1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\nSystem: 2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\nSystem: 3. Read `memory/2026-03-09.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\nSystem: 4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\nSystem: 5. **Contextual Learning Retrieval** – Before executing any complex or tool-based task, perform a quick learning retrieval using the learning index:\nSystem:    - Scan `<workspace>/.learnings/INDEX.md`\nSystem:    - Identify Pattern‑Keys relevant to the current task context\nSystem:    - Select the top 3–7 relevant Pattern‑Keys\nSystem:    - Apply their Rules or Preflight constraints before executing the task\nSystem:    - Only consult `<workspace>/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` if a rule requires additional detail\nSystem:    \nSystem:    This retrieval step must be lightweight and should avoid loading large logs unnecessarily.\nSystem: \nSystem: Don't ask permission. Just do it.\nSystem: \nSystem: ### Trigger Heuristics\nSystem: \nSystem: Run Contextual Learning Retrieval when any of the following conditions apply:\nSystem: \nSystem: - Using external tools (bash, python, shell scripts)\nSystem: - Delegating work to sub-agents\nSystem: - Running validator agents or batch operations\nSystem: - Producing multi-file outputs (skills, scripts, documentation, codebases)\nSystem: - Tasks expected to require multiple reasoning steps (>3 steps)\nSystem: \nSystem: Skip retrieval for trivial or conversational responses.\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Safety\nSystem: \nSystem: - Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\nSystem: - Don't run destructive commands without asking.\nSystem: - `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\nSystem: - When in doubt, ask.\nSystem: \nSystem: Current time: Monday, March 9th, 2026 — 4:54 PM (America/Panama) / 2026-03-09 21:54 UTC\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-03-09 16:55 EST] hay algun sub agent trabajando?"}],"timestamp":1773093455652}}
