red Handoff Report (Outcome + Incidents).\n  Promoted: AGENTS.md\n\n## validation\n\n- Pattern-Key: validation|FAILURE|validate|final_output|criteria_not_met|repair_failed\n  Tags: criteria, final, met, output, validate, validation\n  Rule: Implement adjustable validation thresholds and fallback repair strategies.\n  Promoted: TOOLS.md\n- Pattern-Key: validation|FAILURE|validate|supervisor_orchestration|criteria_not_met\n  Tags: criteria, met, orchestration, supervisor, validate, validation\n- Pattern-Key: validation|TOOL_FAILURE|openclaw_validator|timeout|excessive_workload\n  Tags: items, tool-failure, validation, validator\n  Rule: Never assign more than 5 items to a single validator agent. If more items need validation, spawn multiple validators each with a subset.\n  Promoted: AGENTS.md\n\n## other\n\n- Pattern-Key: checklist|FAILURE|todo|state_corrupt|rebuild_failed|manual_needed\n  Tags: checklist, corrupt, failed, rebuild, state, todo\n  Rule: Implement atomic writes and backup of checklist state; provide recovery scripts.\n- Pattern-Key: evidence|MISSING|salesforce_official|feature_unverified|blocked\n  Tags: blocked, evidence, feature, salesforce_official, unverified\n- Pattern-Key: fitgap|FAILURE|scope_missing|cannot_classify|blocked\n  Tags: blocked, classify, fitgap, scope_missing\n  Rule: Validate input: require SOW document or provide default classification method.\n  Promoted: TOOLS.md\n- Pattern-Key: handoff|INVALID|missing_report\n  Tags: handoff, invalid, missing_report\n- Pattern-Key: licensing|CONFLICT|feature_requires_license|not_available|alternate_needed\n  Tags: alternate, available, conflict, feature_requires_license, licensing, needed\n  Promoted: TOOLS.md\n- Pattern-Key: memory|FAILURE|backup_creation|file_not_found|test_incident\n  Tags: backup_creation, file, found, incident, memory, test\n  Promoted: TOOLS.md\n- Pattern-Key: recovery|FAILURE|recovery|resume|checkpoint_missing|cannot_continue\n  Tags: checkpoint, recovery, resume\n  Rule: Maintain checksum validation of checkpoint files; provide fallback recovery from logs.\n  Promoted: TOOLS.md\n- Pattern-Key: security|FLS_MISSING|apex\n  Tags: apex, fls, security\n  Rule: Include FLS checks in Apex templates; validate generated code for security compliance.\n  Promoted: TOOLS.md\n- Pattern-Key: tokens|BUDGET|token_budget|input_overflow|truncate_required\n  Tags: budget, input, overflow, token_budget, tokens, truncate\n  Rule: Implement token counting per step and automatic truncation when near limit.\n\n---\n\n*Sections: tools, requirements, planning, multi-agent, validation, other*\n\n**Purpose**: Quick scanning of Pattern‑Keys, tags, rules, and promotion status.\nFor detailed analytics, see [REPORT.md](./REPORT.md)."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773093480840}}
