ion. Just do it.\n\n### Trigger Heuristics\n\nRun Contextual Learning Retrieval when any of the following conditions apply:\n\n- Using external tools (bash, python, shell scripts)\n- Delegating work to sub-agents\n- Running validator agents or batch operations\n- Producing multi-file outputs (skills, scripts, documentation, codebases)\n- Tasks expected to require multiple reasoning steps (>3 steps)\n\nSkip retrieval for trivial or conversational responses.\n\n## Safety\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"b5aa5cb5","tokensBefore":109669,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/openclaw/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/46f0b5c5-6825-4975-8ac5-ec1d615a501c.jsonl","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/INDEX.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/projects.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/MAIN_AGENT_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/SKILL.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/scripts/distributed_orchestrate.py","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/scripts/orchestrate.py","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/scripts/plan_generator.py","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/weather/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-09.md"]},"fromHook":true}
