{"type":"message","id":"7fddce7a","parentId":"8659c8cd","timestamp":"2026-03-09T23:59:44.162Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **4. PRODUCTION_CERTIFICATION_MATRIX.md**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_76B7Zn01iWXkiEKSik2a7hOG","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/system_validation/PRODUCTION_CERTIFICATION_MATRIX.md","content":"# PRODUCTION_CERTIFICATION_MATRIX.md\n# Current Production Readiness Status of OpenClaw Skills\n# Last updated: 2026-03-09\n# Based on Operational Reinforcement Initiative\n\n## MATRIX LEGEND\n\n### Certification Levels:\n- **🟢 PRODUCTION-READY**: All criteria met, suitable for production use\n- **🟡 DEVELOPMENT-READY**: Functional but not fully production-proven\n- **🟠 PARTIAL**: Some functionality exists, clear limitations\n- **🔴 SIMULATED**: Outputs descriptive only, no real execution\n- **⚫ BROKEN**: Invocation fails or critical functions missing\n- **⚪ NOT VERIFIED**: Insufficient testing evidence\n\n### Risk Levels:\n- **HIGH**: Critical gap affecting core functionality\n- **MEDIUM**: Significant limitation affecting usability\n- **LOW**: Minor limitation or edge case\n- **NONE**: No known issues\n\n---\n\n## CURRENT CERTIFICATION STATUS\n\n| Skill | Certification | Last Tested | Core Risk | Integration Risk | Production Status |\n|-------|--------------|-------------|-----------|------------------|-------------------|\n| **long-prompt-orchestrator** | 🟠 PARTIAL | 2026-03-09 | HIGH | HIGH | ❌ NOT READY |\n| **agent-watchdog** | 🟠 PARTIAL | 2026-03-09 | HIGH | HIGH | ❌ NOT READY |\n| **salesforce-code-auditor** | 🟠 PARTIAL | 2026-03-09 | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | ❌ NOT READY |\n| **salesforce-architect** | 🟢 PRODUCTION-READY | 2026-03-09 | LOW | LOW | ✅ READY |\n| **workspace-janitor** | 🟢 PRODUCTION-READY | 2026-03-09 | LOW | LOW | ✅ READY |\n| **error-learning-loop** | 🟢 PRODUCTION-READY | 2026-03-09 | LOW | LOW | ✅ READY |\n| **vector-memory** | 🟢 PRODUCTION-READY | 2026-03-09 | LOW | LOW | ✅ READY |\n| **tavily-web-search** | 🟢 PRODUCTION-READY | 2026-03-09 | LOW | LOW | ✅ READY |\n| **OC-Intent-Governor** | 🟢 PRODUCTION-READY | 2026-03-09 | LOW | LOW | ✅ READY |\n| **OC-Respawner** | 🟠 PARTIAL | 2026-03-09 | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | ❌ NOT READY |\n| **OC-System-Evolver** | 🟠 PARTIAL | 2026-03-09 | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | ❌ NOT READY |\n\n---\n\n## DETAILED CERTIFICATION ANALYSIS\n\n### 🟠 long-prompt-orchestrator (PARTIAL)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Generates JSON plans from prompts\n- ✅ Estimates resources (tokens, time)\n- ❌ Plans not executable (abstract tasks)\n- ❌ No real distributed execution enablement\n\n**Integration**: 🔴 BROKEN\n- ❌ Cannot delegate to real sub-agents\n- ❌ Main must manually translate plans\n- ❌ No real handoff mechanism\n\n**Error Handling**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Basic input validation\n- ❌ No recovery for plan execution failures\n\n**Production Readiness**: ❌ NOT READY\n- **Critical Gap**: Plans are not actionable\n- **Risk**: HIGH - Core purpose not fulfilled\n- **Fix Required**: Convert plans to executable format\n\n### 🟠 agent-watchdog (PARTIAL)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Recovery logic exists in code\n- ❌ No real monitoring implementation\n- ❌ No monitored objects/sessions\n\n**Integration**: 🔴 BROKEN\n- ❌ No integration with real agent sessions\n- ❌ No monitoring directory or logs\n- ❌ Recovery never triggered\n\n**Error Handling**: ⚪ NOT VERIFIED\n- ❓ Unknown how failures are handled\n\n**Production Readiness**: ❌ NOT READY\n- **Critical Gap**: No real observability\n- **Risk**: HIGH - Monitoring is simulated\n- **Fix Required**: Implement real session monitoring\n\n### 🟠 salesforce-code-auditor (PARTIAL)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Scripts exist and can be invoked\n- ❌ Not tested with real Salesforce metadata\n- ❌ Unknown if generates substantive findings\n\n**Integration**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Documented integration with architect\n- ❌ Not verified with real data flow\n- ❌ Unknown if