al system stable\n- **Recommendation**: Monitor incident volume\n\n### 🟢 vector-memory (PRODUCTION-READY)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ Memory curation works\n- ✅ Backup creation functional\n- ✅ Semantic search operational (after fix)\n\n**Integration**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ PostgreSQL integration works\n- ✅ Gemini embeddings functional\n- ✅ Filesystem integration verified\n\n**Error Handling**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ Dry-run mode available\n- ✅ Backup/restore capability\n- ✅ Graceful degradation\n\n**Production Readiness**: ✅ READY\n- **Status**: Fully operational (post-fix)\n- **Risk**: LOW - Recently repaired and verified\n- **Recommendation**: Monitor embedding performance\n\n### 🟢 tavily-web-search (PRODUCTION-READY)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ Web search works\n- ✅ Content extraction functional\n- ✅ Research capabilities operational\n\n**Integration**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ Watchdog registration works\n- ✅ Error-learning-loop integration\n- ✅ Janitor cache cleanup verified\n\n**Error Handling**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ Rate limit handling\n- ✅ Cache fallback mode\n- ✅ Exponential backoff retry\n\n**Production Readiness**: ✅ READY\n- **Status**: Fully operational\n- **Risk**: LOW - Well-integrated ecosystem\n- **Recommendation**: Monitor API credit usage\n\n### 🟢 OC-Intent-Governor (PRODUCTION-READY)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ Intent parsing works\n- ✅ Entity extraction functional\n- ✅ Risk detection operational\n\n**Integration**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Script execution works\n- ❌ Integration with other skills not verified\n\n**Error Handling**: 🟢 COMPLETE\n- ✅ Input validation works\n- ✅ Clear error messages\n\n**Production Readiness**: ✅ READY (with caveat)\n- **Status**: Core functionality ready\n- **Risk**: LOW - Standalone tool works\n- **Recommendation**: Verify integration use cases\n\n### 🟠 OC-Respawner (PARTIAL)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Scripts exist\n- ❌ Functionality not verified\n- ❌ Unknown if validation works\n\n**Integration**: ⚪ NOT VERIFIED\n- ❓ Unknown integration capabilities\n\n**Error Handling**: ⚪ NOT VERIFIED\n- ❓ Unknown failure handling\n\n**Production Readiness**: ❌ NOT READY\n- **Critical Gap**: Untested functionality\n- **Risk**: MEDIUM - Unknown operational state\n- **Fix Required**: Basic operational testing\n\n### 🟠 OC-System-Evolver (PARTIAL)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Improvement proposals generated\n- ✅ System observation works\n- ❌ Limited testing evidence\n\n**Integration**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Cron job integration works\n- ❌ Depth of analysis unknown\n\n**Error Handling**: ⚪ NOT VERIFIED\n- ❓ Unknown failure handling\n\n**Production Readiness**: ❌ NOT READY\n- **Critical Gap**: Limited operational proof\n- **Risk**: MEDIUM - Functionality uncertain\n- **Fix Required**: More comprehensive testing\n\n---\n\n## PRODUCTION ECOSYSTEM READINESS\n\n### ✅ READY FOR PRODUCTION (6 skills):\n- salesforce-architect\n- workspace-janitor  \n- error-learning-loop\n- vector-memory\n- tavily-web-search\n- OC-Intent-Governor\n\n### ❌ NOT READY FOR PRODUCTION (5 skills):\n- long-prompt-orchestrator (CRITICAL)\n- agent-watchdog (CRITICAL)\n- salesforce-code-auditor (HIGH)\n- OC-Respawner (MEDIUM)\n- OC-System-Evolver (MEDIUM)\n\n### OVERALL ECOSYSTEM STATUS: 🟡 PARTIALLY READY\n- **Core Infrastructure**: ✅ READY (memory, error handling, janitor)\n- **Critical Orchestration**: ❌ NOT READY (LPO, watchdog)\n- **Specialized Tools**: 🟡 MIXED (Salesforce ready, others partial)\n- **Integration Health**: 🟡 PARTIAL (some gaps in critical paths)\n\n---\n\n## IMMEDIATE CERTIFICATION ACTIONS REQUIRED\n\n### Priority 1 (CRITICAL):\n1. **Fix long-prompt-orchestrator**: Make plans executable\n2. **Fix agent-watchdog**: Implement real monitoring\n\n### Priority 2 (HIGH):\n3. **Test salesforce-code-auditor** with real fixtures\n4. **Verify OC-Respawner** basic functionality\n\n### Priority 3 (MEDIUM):\n5. **Expand OC-System-Evolver** testing\n6. **Verify OC-Intent-Governor** integrations\n\n### Priority 4 (LOW):\n7. **Document limitations** of partial skills\n8. **Create recertification schedule**\n\n---\n\n## NEXT CERTIFICATION REVIEW\n**Scheduled**: 2026-03-16 (7 days)\n**Focus**: Priority 1 and 2 fixes\n**Success Criteria**: At least 2 skills moved from PARTIAL to FUNCTIONAL"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":62,"output":2713,"cacheRead":93824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773100709143}}
