{"type":"message","id":"8abee6fd","parentId":"a76c1231","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:04:56.084Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📋 **RESUMEN DE DISTRIBUCIÓN DE FIXES**\n\n### **✅ WORKSTREAM A COMPLETADO (Main Agent):**\n- **Framework de Validación creado**: 6 archivos fundamentales\n- **One-time foundation establecida**: Criterios REAL vs SIMULATED definidos\n- **Estado actual documentado**: Matriz de certificación actualizada\n\n### **🚀 WORKSTREAMS B-E DISTRIBUIDOS (4 Sub-agents):**\n\n#### **1. LPO Executable Plan Fix Specialist**\n- **Task**: Convertir planes abstractos → planes ejecutables\n- **Target**: `long-prompt-orchestrator`\n- **Success Criteria**: Plans usable by main agent sin traducción manual\n- **Session**: `agent:main:subagent:e96b4060-87f4-4a0a-a343-69fd012a92b5`\n\n#### **2. Watchdog Reality Implementation Specialist**\n- **Task**: Implementar monitoreo REAL (no simulado)\n- **Target**: `agent-watchdog`\n- **Success Criteria**: Real observabilidad con logs/artifacts reales\n- **Session**: `agent:main:subagent:487e7d69-131b-4837-9fca-5cc299ee4db4`\n\n#### **3. Salesforce Auditor Reality Tester**\n- **Task**: Probar con fixtures REALES de Salesforce\n- **Target**: `salesforce-code-auditor`\n- **Success Criteria**: Findings sustantivos de código real (no placeholders)\n- **Session**: `agent:main:subagent:71f6ae19-15fd-4b6c-a446-3af75a427b2d`\n\n#### **4. Salesforce Integration Validator**\n- **Task**: Validar integración REAL architect ↔ auditor\n- **Target**: Integración Salesforce ecosystem\n- **Success Criteria**: Real data flow entre"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1773101067251,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted"}}
