 retrieval step must be lightweight and should avoid loading large logs unnecessarily.\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n### Trigger Heuristics\n\nRun Contextual Learning Retrieval when any of the following conditions apply:\n\n- Using external tools (bash, python, shell scripts)\n- Delegating work to sub-agents\n- Running validator agents or batch operations\n- Producing multi-file outputs (skills, scripts, documentation, codebases)\n- Tasks expected to require multiple reasoning steps (>3 steps)\n\nSkip retrieval for trivial or conversational responses.\n\n## Safety\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"b592b90f","tokensBefore":108313,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/INDEX.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/projects.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/OC-Respawner/scripts/validate_environment.py","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/scripts/watchdog_recovery.py","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/vector-memory/scripts/memory_auto_curate.py"],"modifiedFiles":["/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-09.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/projects/openclaw_operational_reinforcement/OPERATIONAL_REINFORCEMENT_PROMPT.txt","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/projects/openclaw_real_capability_audit/AUDIT_PROMPT.txt","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/projects/openclaw_real_capability_audit/OPENCLAW_REAL_CAPABILITY_AUDIT_REPORT.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/projects/openclaw_real_capability_audit/README.md","/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/projects/openclaw_real_capability_audit/distributed_t