{"type":"message","id":"4a5bb54d","parentId":"c936bdcb","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:27:18.852Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **2. Sub-agent para Integrar Sistema de Monitoreo REAL en Workflows:**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_oPwjSnUstgN1MwuT0gpfYCfU","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"# TASK: Integrate Real Monitoring System into OpenClaw Workflows\n\n## CONTEXT\nThe `agent-watchdog` skill now has REAL monitoring infrastructure:\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/.watchdog/` directory with real data\n- Real session discovery and tracking\n- Observable logs and metrics\n- Real stall detection and recovery\n\n## YOUR MISSION\nIntegrate this REAL monitoring system into existing OpenClaw workflows.\n\n## SPECIFIC REQUIREMENTS\n\n### 1. Integrate with Main Agent Workflows\n- Add monitoring registration to main agent task execution\n- Track main agent sessions and sub-agent spawns\n- Monitor task progress and completion\n- Detect stalls in main agent operations\n\n### 2. Integrate with Sub-agent System\n- Register sub-agents with watchdog when spawned\n- Track sub-agent execution time and progress\n- Monitor for sub-agent stalls\n- Enable recovery for stalled sub-agents\n\n### 3. Integrate with Cron Jobs\n- Monitor cron job executions\n- Track cron job success/failure\n- Detect stalled cron jobs\n- Enable recovery for failed cron jobs\n\n### 4. Create Monitoring Dashboard\n- Simple dashboard showing system health\n- Active sessions and their status\n- Recent incidents and recoveries\n- Performance metrics\n\n### 5. Enable Real-time Alerts\n- Alert for critical stalls (>5 minutes)\n- Alert for repeated failures\n- Alert for system resource issues\n- Integration with error-learning-loop\n\n## ANTI-SIMULATION RULES\n- NO simulated monitoring integration\n- REAL session registration required\n- REAL progress tracking required\n- REAL alert generation required\n- Observable evidence required\n\n## INTEGRATION POINTS TO MODIFY\n\n### 1. Main Agent Integration\n- Modify main agent to register with watchdog\n- Add monitoring calls to task execution\n- Enable stall detection for long operations\n\n### 2. Sub-agent Spawn Integration\n- Modify `sessions_spawn` to register sub-agents\n- Add monitoring to sub-agent execution\n- Enable recovery for stalled sub-agents\n\n### 3. Cron Job Integration\n- Add monitoring to cron job execution\n- Track cron job performance\n- Enable recovery for failed cron jobs\n\n## FILES TO CREATE/MODIFY\n1. `integration/main_agent_monitoring.py` - Main agent integration\n2. `integration/subagent_monitoring.py` - Sub-agent integration\n3. `integration/cron_monitoring.py` - Cron job integration\n4. `dashboard/monitoring_dashboard.py` - Simple dashboard\n5. `alerts/real_time_alerts.py` - Alert system\n6. Update existing workflows to include monitoring\n\n## DELIVERABLES\n1. **Integrated monitoring system** working with all workflows\n2. **Evidence** showing:\n   - Main agent sessions being monitored\n   - Sub-agents registered and tracked\n   - Cron jobs monitored\n   - Real alerts generated\n   - Recovery actions triggered\n3. **Monitoring dashboard** showing real data\n4. **Handoff report** with integration evidence\n\n## SUCCESS CRITERIA\nMonitoring is **FULLY INTEGRATED** when:\n1. Main agent workflows include monitoring\n2. Sub-agents are automatically registered\n3. Cron jobs are monitored\n4. Real alerts work\n5. Dashboard shows real monitoring data\n\n## TIMELINE\n- Start: Immediate\n- Complete: Within 30 minutes\n- Report: Concise handoff with integration evidence\n\nProceed to integrate REAL monitoring into all OpenClaw workflows.","label":"Monitoring System Integrator","runtime":"subagent","model":"deepseek-chat"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":220,"output":846,"cacheRead":47488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48554,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773102411778}}
{"type":"message","id":"759645c1","parentId":"4a5bb54d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:27:19.040Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_oPwjSnUstgN1MwuT0gpfYCfU","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:ea731592-30ae-4fb4-85f5-bd459a5159e9\",\n  \"runId\": \"19c0f4cf-f36f-4c92-a29b-5096a7767cdd\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}"}],"details":{"status":"accepted","childSessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:ea731592-30ae-4fb4-85f5-bd459a5159e9","runId":"19c0f4cf-f36f-4c92-a29b-5096a7767cdd","mode":"run","note":"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.","modelApplied":true},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773102439036}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0f461d0","parentId":"759645c1","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:27:46.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **3. Sub-agent para Validar Fix de `long-prompt-orchestrator` con Test de Integración REAL:**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_mjfIXDaMZiP6Ynih8VEutZhb","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"# TASK: Validate LPO Fix with Real Integration Test (Main Agent)\n\n## CONTEXT\nThe `long-prompt-orchestrator` skill has been fixed to generate **executable plans**. Now we need to validate that:\n1. Main agent can actually USE the new executable plans\n2. Plans work in real integration scenarios\n3. No manual translation is required\n\n## YOUR MISSION\nExecute a REAL integration test where main agent uses LPO-generated executable plans.\n\n## TEST SCENARIO\nCreate and test this workflow:\n1. **LPO generates executable plan** for a real task\n2. **Main agent parses and executes** plan without manual translation\n3. **Tasks are completed** based on plan instructions\n4. **Artifacts are created** as specified in plan\n5. **Validation occurs** as defined in plan\n\n## SPECIFIC TEST REQUIREMENTS\n\n### Test 1: Basic Plan Execution\n- LPO generates plan for \"Inventory workspace skills\"\n- Plan includes: `execution_mode: \"main\"`, `action_type: \"exec\"`, `action_instructions: \"find ...\"`\n- Main agent executes plan directly\n- Verify artifacts created\n\n### Test 2: Mixed Execution Plan\n- LPO generates plan with both `main` and `subagent` tasks\n- Plan includes dependencies between tasks\n- Main agent executes main tasks, spawns sub-agents for subagent tasks\n- Verify all tasks complete in correct order\n\n### Test 3: Complex Orchestration\n- LPO generates plan for multi-step audit task\n- Plan includes skill invocations, file operations, validations\n- Main agent orchestrates complete execution\n- Verify end-to-end workflow success\n\n## ANTI-SIMULATION RULES\n- NO manual translation of plan by you\n- Main agent MUST execute plan directly\n- NO placeholder artifacts\n- REAL execution evidence required\n- NO fake task completions\n\n## TEST METHODOLOGY\n1. **Generate plan**: Use fixed LPO to create executable plan\n2. **Execute as main**: Simulate main agent executing plan\n3. **Collect evidence**: Logs, artifacts, completion status\n4. **Validate**: Check all plan tasks completed as specified\n\n## DELIVERABLES\n1. **Test evidence** showing:\n   - LPO-generated executable plan (full content)\n   - Main agent parsing and understanding plan\n   - Execution logs showing tasks being completed\n   - Artifacts created as specified in plan\n   - Validation results\n2. **Integration test report** with:\n   - Success/failure of each test scenario\n   - Evidence of no manual translation required\n   - Proof that plans are truly executable\n3. **Handoff report** with validation outcome\n\n## SUCCESS CRITERIA\nLPO fix is **VALIDATED** when:\n1. Main agent can parse and execute LPO plans directly\n2. No manual translation or interpretation required\n3. All plan tasks complete as specified\n4. Artifacts created match plan specifications\n5. Evidence shows real execution, not simulation\n\n## FAILURE CRITERIA\nLPO fix is **NOT VALIDATED** if:\n1. Manual translation still required\n2. Plans contain abstract objectives\n3. Main agent cannot execute tasks directly\n4. Evidence shows simulation, not real execution\n\n## TIMELINE\n- Start: Immediate\n- Complete: Within 30 minutes\n- Report: Concise handoff with test evidence\n\nProceed to validate the LPO fix with REAL integration testing.","label":"LPO Integration Validator","runtime":"subagent","model":"deepseek-chat"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":232,"output":852,"cacheRead":48512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49596,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773102439039}}
