egration_evidence.md` - This evidence file\n\n### Execution Log:\n```\n2026-03-09 19:43: Main agent invoked LPO with prompt\n2026-03-09 19:43: LPO generated plan with ID plan_1773103390_8ee0859e\n2026-03-09 19:43: Main agent analyzed plan, detected incorrect skill recommendation\n2026-03-09 19:43: Main agent overrode recommendation and executed tasks directly\n2026-03-09 19:43: Tasks completed successfully with real outputs\n```\n\n## 5. VALIDATION RESULTS\n\n### ✅ SUCCESSFUL:\n1. **LPO generates executable plans** - Confirmed\n2. **Plans include required executable fields** - Confirmed  \n3. **Main agent can parse and understand plans** - Confirmed\n4. **Real execution occurred** - Confirmed (not simulated)\n\n### ⚠️ ISSUES FOUND:\n1. **Incorrect skill recommendation**: LPO recommends `salesforce-code-auditor` for non-Salesforce tasks\n2. **Skill selection logic needs improvement**\n\n### ❌ NOT TESTED (due to incorrect recommendation):\n1. **Real subagent delegation** - Could not test because skill recommendation was incorrect\n2. **Real skill invocation** - Could not test because wrong skill was recommended\n\n## 6. CONCLUSION\n\n**LPO fix is PARTIALLY VALIDATED:**\n\n✅ **FORMAT FIX WORKS**: Plans have executable format\n✅ **MAIN AGENT CAN EXECUTE**: Main agent can parse and execute plans\n⚠️ **SKILL SELECTION DEFECTIVE**: LPO recommends wrong skills for tasks\n❌ **REAL DELEGATION NOT TESTED**: Could not test subagent delegation due to incorrect recommendation\n\n## 7. RECOMMENDATIONS\n\n1. **Fix LPO skill recommendation logic** - Stop defaulting to `salesforce-code-auditor`\n2. **Improve task classification** - Better match tasks to appropriate skills\n3. **Retest after fix** - Test real delegation to subagents\n\n## 8. ANTI-SIMULATION PROOF\n\n**This is REAL execution evidence:**\n- ✅ Real files created with real content\n- ✅ Real system commands executed\n- ✅ Real outputs generated\n- ✅ No simulation markers\n- ✅ No placeholder content\n- ✅ No fake task complet