ts\n3. **Establish monitoring metrics** for system health\n\n---\n\n## EVIDENCE ARCHIVE\n\nAll operational evidence preserved in:\n- Project: `/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/projects/openclaw_operational_reinforcement/`\n- System Validation: `/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/system_validation/`\n- Watchdog Monitoring: `~/.openclaw/workspace/.watchdog/`\n- Test Artifacts: Various `/tmp/` files with real execution evidence\n\n---\n\n**Report End**  \n*Operational reinforcement"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":8550,"output":4096,"cacheRead":62784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"length","timestamp":1773104326211}}
