{"type":"message","id":"274b31ca","parentId":"9adbb94d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:21:29.864Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 🎯 **CYCLE 1: RE-AUDIT ALL COMPONENTS AFTER FIXES**\n\n### **📊 SYSTEM STATUS TABLE (RE-AUDIT)**\n\n| Component | Classification | Real Evidence | Main Risk | Blocker |\n|-----------|----------------|---------------|-----------|---------|\n| `long-prompt-orchestrator` | PARTIAL | ⚠️ Plans executable but content simulated for complex tasks | Medium | Defect: Echo statements instead of real instructions |\n| `agent-watchdog` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Real monitoring logs, dashboard, alerts | Low | None |\n| `salesforce-code-auditor` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Complete reports, real findings, risk assessment | Low | None |\n| `salesforce-architect` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Stable, real integration verified | None | None |\n| `workspace-janitor` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Stable, operational | None | None |\n| `error-learning-loop` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Stable, incident emission works | None | None |\n| `vector-memory` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Stable, semantic search works | None | None |\n| `tavily-web-search` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Stable, web search works | None | None |\n| `OC-Intent-Governor` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Stable, governance works | None | None |\n| `OC-System-Evolver` | FUNCTIONAL | ✅ Real system analysis, improvement proposals | Low | None (cron duplication fixed) |\n| `OC-Respawner` | PARTIAL | ✅ Real environment validation, migration planning | Medium | Focus: Migration planning, not real-time respawn |\n\n### **🎯 IMMEDIATE FIX PLAN (CYCLE 2)**\n\n| Fix ID | Component | Problem | Decision | Owner | Real Validation Needed |\n|--------|-----------|---------|----------|-------|------------------------|\n| **FIX-005** | `long-prompt-orchestrator` | Echo statements for complex tasks (simulation pattern) | FIX_NOW | Sub-agent | Real conversion: abstract objectives → executable instructions |\n| **FIX-006** | `OC-Respawner` | Misclassification: Migration planning vs real-time respawn | FIX_NOW | Main | Reclassification documentation |\n\n### **🔧 FIX DISTRIBUTION PLAN (CYCLE 2)**\n\n#### **Sub-agent: LPO Complex Task Fixer**\n- **Fix ID**: FIX-005\n- **Component**: `long-prompt-orchestrator`\n- **Exact Problem**: Converts complex objectives to echo statements (simulation)\n- **Files**: `plan_generator.py`, `distributed_orchestrate.py`\n- **Expected Outcome**: Convert \"Validates 9 FUNCTIONAL components\" → specific validation instructions\n- **Validation**: Real prompt with complex objective → executable plan (no echo statements)\n- **Evidence**: Before/after plan comparison showing real instructions\n- **Prerequisites**: None\n\n#### **Main Agent: OC-Respawner Reclassifier**\n- **Fix ID**: FIX-006\n- **Component**: `OC-Respawner`\n- **Exact Problem**: Misclassified as respawn system, actually migration planning\n- **Action**: Update documentation, reclassify honestly\n- **Expected Outcome**: Clear classification as \"Migration Planning System\"\n- **Validation**: Documentation matches real capability\n- **Evidence**: Updated SKILL.md with honest capability description\n\n### **📈 FIX EXECUTION RESULTS (CYCLE 1)**\n\n#### **✅ COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY:**\n1. **FIX-001**: `OC-System-Evolver` validated as FUNCTIONAL (real operational scenarios)\n2. **FIX-002**: `OC-Respawner` evaluated honestly as PARTIAL (migration planning)\n3. **FIX-003**: Cron job duplication fixed (07:00 AM Linux cron removed)\n4. **FIX-004**: LPO test revealed simulation defect with complex tasks\n\n#### **🔄 IN PROGRESS (CYCLE 2):**\n1. **FIX-005**: LPO complex task fix\n2. **FIX-006**: OC-Respawner reclassification\n\n### **✅ VALIDATION RESULTS (RE-AUDIT)**\n\n#### **Anti-Simulation Check PASSED:**\n- ✅ No fake IDs, handoffs, or simulated evidence in validated components\n- ✅ All evidence operational (logs, artifacts, real execution)\n- ✅ Honest classification of limitations\n\n#### **Simulation Detected and Documented:**\n- ❌ `long-prompt-orchestrator`: Echo statements for complex tasks (simulation pattern)\n- ✅ **Documented honestly** as PARTIAL with specific defect\n\n#### **Integration Validation:**\n- ✅ `agent-watchdog` ↔ monitoring system: REAL integration\n- ✅ `salesforce-architect` ↔ `salesforce-code-auditor`: REAL integration\n- ✅ `error-learning-loop` ↔ incident emission: REAL integration\n\n### **🚫 REAL VALIDATION BLOCKERS**\n\n**None currently.** All components can be validated in current environment.\n\n### **🔍 RE-AUDIT SUMMARY**\n\n#### **Progress Since Cycle Start:**\n- **Initial**: 5 PARTIAL components, 1 SIMULATED integration\n- **Cycle 1 Complete**: 2 PARTIAL components, 0 SIMULATED (except LPO defect)\n- **Improvement**: 3 components moved to FUNCTIONAL, 1 simulation eliminated\n\n#### **Current State:**\n- **FUNCTIONAL**: 9 components (82%)\n- **PARTIAL**: 2 components (18%) - honestly classified with specific reasons\n- **SIMULATED**: 0 components (except LPO defect being fixed)\n\n#### **Anti-Simulation Enforcement:**\n- ✅ Simulation detected and documented (LPO echo statements)\n- ✅ No hidden simulation accepted\n- ✅ Honest classification maintained\n\n### **🔄 NEXT CYCLE DECISION**\n\n**CONTINUE_CYCLE**\n\n#### **Reason:**\n- 1 critical component (`long-prompt-orchestrator`) has simulation defect\n- Termination condition not met: \"No component is SIMULATED\" (LPO has simulation pattern)\n- Real fix possible and assigned\n\n#### **Cycle 2 Focus:**\n1. **Fix LPO simulation defect** (echo statements → real instructions)\n2. **Reclassify OC-Respawner** honestly as migration planning system\n3. **Re-audit after fixes** to verify simulation eliminated\n\n### **🎯 CREATING SUB-AGENT FOR LPO FIX:**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_jnuXBztmDRObu1CZ2UFARvPY","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"# TASK: Fix LPO Simulation Defect - Echo Statements for Complex Tasks\n\n## CONTEXT\nThe `long-prompt-orchestrator` skill has a critical simulation defect:\n\n**PROBLEM**: When faced with complex tasks, LPO generates echo statements instead of real executable instructions.\n\n**EVIDENCE FROM REAL TEST**:\n- Prompt: \"Validates the 9 FUNCTIONAL components remain functional\"\n- LPO generated: `echo 'Starting task: Validates the 9 FUNCTIONAL components remain functional...' date`\n- This is **SIMULATION** according to anti-simulation rules\n\n**ANTI-SIMULATION RULE VIOLATED**:\n- Rule 3: \"No synthetic runtime evidence\" - Echo statements are synthetic\n- Rule 5: \"No hidden manual completion\" - Main agent would have to fill in real validation\n- Pattern 1: \"Descriptive Outputs\" - Describes what WOULD happen, not what DID happen\n\n## YOUR MISSION\nFix LPO to convert complex objectives → specific executable instructions, NOT echo statements.\n\n## SPECIFIC REQUIREMENTS\n\n### 1. Analyze Current Defect\nExamine why LPO falls back to echo statements for complex tasks like:\n- \"Validates the 9 FUNCTIONAL components remain functional\"\n- \"Tests anti-simulation framework effectiveness\"\n- \"Creates monitoring dashboard for audit status\"\n\n### 2. Implement Real Instruction Generation\nCreate logic to convert abstract objectives → specific executable instructions:\n\n**Example Conversion:**\n- **Input**: \"Validates the 9 FUNCTIONAL components remain functional\"\n- **Current (SIMULATED)**: `echo 'Starting task...' date`\n- **Required (REAL)**: \n  ```\n  # Validate long-prompt-orchestrator\n  python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/scripts/orchestrate.py --prompt \"Test prompt\" --output-file /tmp/lpo_test.json\n  \n  # Validate agent-watchdog\n  python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-watchdog/scripts/watchdog_monitor_real.py --status\n  \n  # Validate salesforce-code-auditor\n  python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/salesforce-code-auditor/scripts/test_reporting_layer.py\n  \n  # [Continue for all 9 components...]\n  ```\n\n### 3. Handle Different Task Types\nCreate mappings for common complex task patterns:\n\n#### Validation Tasks:\n- \"Validates X\" → specific validation commands for X\n- \"Tests Y\" → specific test commands for Y\n- \"Checks Z\" → specific check commands for Z\n\n#### Creation Tasks:\n- \"Creates dashboard\" → specific dashboard creation commands\n- \"Generates report\" → specific report generation commands\n- \"Establishes schedule\" → specific scheduling commands\n\n### 4. Preserve Existing Functionality\n- Keep working simple task conversion\n- Maintain skill recommendation logic (already fixed)\n- Don't break existing functionality\n\n## ANTI-SIMULATION RULES (ABSOLUTE)\n- NO echo statements as action_instructions\n- NO placeholder content\n- REAL executable instructions required\n- Evidence must show before/after comparison\n\n## FILES TO MODIFY\n1. `plan_generator.py` - Task generation logic\n2. `distributed_orchestrate.py` - Task analysis logic\n3. Add helper functions for complex task decomposition\n\n## DELIVERABLES\n1. **Fixed code** with real instruction generation\n2. **Test evidence** showing:\n   - Before: Echo statements for complex tasks\n   - After: Specific executable instructions\n   - Real prompt → real plan → real execution capability\n3. **Updated documentation** reflecting fix\n4. **Handoff report** with anti-simulation compliance evidence\n\n## SUCCESS CRITERIA\nLPO simulation defect is **FIXED** when:\n1. Complex tasks generate specific executable instructions (not echo statements)\n2. No simulation patterns in generated plans\n3. Real execution possible from generated plans\n4. Evidence shows before/after improvement\n\n## FAILURE CRITERIA\nFix is **NOT COMPLETE** if:\n1. Echo statements still generated for complex tasks\n2. Simulation patterns persist\n3. No real improvement demonstrated\n\n## TIMELINE\n- Start: Immediate\n- Complete: Within 20 minutes\n- Report: Concise with operational evidence\n\nProceed to eliminate this simulation defect from LPO.","label":"LPO Simulation Defect Fixer","runtime":"subagent","model":"deepseek-chat"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":74,"output":2406,"cacheRead":97984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773105591260}}
