W | LOW | ✅ READY |\n| **OC-Respawner** | 🟠 PARTIAL | 2026-03-09 | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | ❌ NOT READY |\n| **OC-System-Evolver** | 🟠 PARTIAL | 2026-03-09 | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | ❌ NOT READY |\n\n---\n\n## DETAILED CERTIFICATION ANALYSIS\n\n### 🟠 long-prompt-orchestrator (PARTIAL)\n**Core Functionality**: 🟡 PARTIAL\n- ✅ Generates JSON plans from prompts\n- ✅ Estimates resources (tokens, time)\n- ❌ Plans not executable (abstract tasks)\n- ❌ No real distributed execution enablement\n\n\n[261 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773105725738}}
