{"type":"message","id":"eff446cf","parentId":"5028e87d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:59:50.898Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Fase 3 completada:** Dashboard REAL funcionando.\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 **FASE 4: TEST REAL CON SUB-AGENT**\n\n### **Paso 1: Crear sub-agent para investigación**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_I8cwvlA2bAnoSXxlUYDNwFyf","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"# TASK: Investigate Integration Procedures for OpenClaw Skills\n\n## CONTEXT\nI need to research and document REAL integration procedures for OpenClaw skills. The goal is to understand how skills should actually integrate with each other in production.\n\n## SPECIFIC RESEARCH QUESTIONS:\n\n### 1. Current Integration Patterns\n- What integration patterns currently exist between OpenClaw skills?\n- How do skills communicate with each other (subprocess calls, API, shared files)?\n- What are the success/failure rates of current integrations?\n\n### 2. Best Practices for Skill Integration\n- What are the recommended patterns for skill-to-skill communication?\n- How should error handling work between integrated skills?\n- What about data passing and state management?\n\n### 3. Real Integration Examples\n- Find REAL examples of working integrations in the workspace\n- Document how `salesforce-architect` integrates with `salesforce-code-auditor`\n- Document how `error-learning-loop` integrates with other skills\n\n### 4. Gaps and Recommendations\n- Identify gaps in current integration capabilities\n- Recommend specific improvements\n- Create a simple integration test to validate findings\n\n## DELIVERABLES:\n1. **Research report** with findings on current integration patterns\n2. **Best practices document** for skill integration\n3. **Real integration examples** from workspace\n4. **Gap analysis** and recommendations\n5. **Simple integration test** to validate a working integration\n\n## METHODOLOGY:\n- Examine existing skill code for integration patterns\n- Check documentation and comments\n- Look for actual working examples\n- Test simple integration scenarios\n\n## TIMELINE: 15-20 minutes\n- Research: 10 minutes\n- Documentation: 5 minutes\n- Test creation: 5 minutes\n\n## IMPORTANT: This is a REAL task for testing agent-watchdog monitoring\n- I will be running for 15-20 minutes\n- agent-watchdog should detect and monitor this session\n- Dashboard should show this session as active\n\nProceed with the research.","label":"Integration Procedures Researcher","runtime":"subagent","model":"deepseek-chat","timeoutSeconds":1200}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":94,"output":576,"cacheRead":76928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773107966689}}
